cinst blender -y
cinst audacity -y
cinst lmms -y
cinst obs-studio -y
cinst kdenlive -y
cinst plexmediaserver -y
cinst sonarr -y
cinst kodi -y

#Tools
cinst sharex -y
cinst etcher -y
